He waxes lyrical and avoids making a pizza order in the middle of his poem this time. Kindergarten Champions http://i.imgur.com/SHVbV.jpg We never think of them as kids, but if a big zapper ray were to shrink our champions down to babies, we think they'd be a little like Latheia draws them here. Violent and adorable, as expected. Submissions are flowing in but we need more from you! Get creative and submit your entry to Summoner_Showcase@RiotGames.com to get a bit of that limelight.
